Text2CAD Random-100 Public Generation Package License Notice

This repository contains two kinds of material with different licensing
considerations.

1. Data

The files under data/ include Text2CAD-derived prompts and CAD token sequences.
These materials should be used
under the upstream Text2CAD dataset license terms where applicable.

At the time this package was prepared, the Text2CAD Hugging Face dataset page
listed the dataset license as Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-
ShareAlike 4.0 International (CC BY-NC-SA 4.0):

https://huggingface.co/datasets/SadilKhan/Text2CAD
https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/

Users must verify the upstream Text2CAD license and access conditions from
their own download source before redistribution or use.

